Package oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.dt.patterns.metadata.creator.common

Common creator panels.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ApplicationsBindingPanel This class provides the binding UI for the Applications Panel and Applicatiopns popup creator wizards.
ApplicationsSubheaderTableDecorator This class represents the decorator for the subheader collections table in the title panel.
ApplicationsTableDecorator This class is used to set properties for the collection summary table.
Attribute This class represents an item in the collections table.
AttributeDragSource This class handles a drag from the source.
AttributeDropTarget This class handles a drop on the target node.
AttributeNode This class represents an attribute node in the tree.
AttributesCollection This class represents the collection of Attributes in the binding panel.
AttributeTransfer This class represents the transferable object for an item in the tree.
CommitablePanel A CommitablePanel is a panel capable of being commit()'d.
GenericFormCreatorPanel Generic panel shown to the user in Form creators.
GenericTableCreatorPanel Generic panel shown to the user in Table creators.
GenericTreeCreationPanel Generic DT panel for creating trees.
GenericTreeTableCreationPanel A CommitablePanel capable of showing form children to implement master/detail relations.
ItemHolderHelper This public class helps in creating the items in the collection table.
PanelBinderDefinitionValidator Validation class used as a callback from the "Select a datasouce" window to ensure a Panel datasource is used.
PanelSubheader This class represents a subheader item in the collections table.
SubSection This class represents the Subheader node in the tree in the component layout panel.
TreeLevel Generic "level" in a DT tree.
